249
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:43,947
Penasaran sama ceritanya.

250
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:50,070
Tayangnya setiap Jumat malam, lho.

251
00:17:50,093 --> 00:17:54,526
Kalau gitu, minggu depan kita nonton bareng lagi, yuk.

252
00:17:54,549 --> 00:17:58,095
Oke, ayo.

253
00:17:58,118 --> 00:18:02,356
Mau nggak sambil makan camilan?

254
00:18:02,379 --> 00:18:05,716
Aku yang bawa.

255
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,740
Scene 10: Pembicaraan tentang Libur dan Kerja Paruh Waktu

256
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:13,730
Sudah jam setengah dua belas malam, ya.

257
00:18:13,753 --> 00:18:18,427
Iya, sebaiknya kita tidur sekarang.

258
00:18:18,451 --> 00:18:22,685
Besok kamu bangun jam berapa?

259
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:28,275
Besok aku libur, jadi bangunnya santai.

260
00:18:28,298 --> 00:18:31,238
Asyik!

261
00:18:31,261 --> 00:18:35,830
Aku besok masih kerja paruh waktu.

262
00:18:35,854 --> 00:18:37,891
Eh,

263
00:18:37,914 --> 00:18:41,687
Minggu juga kerja paruh waktu?

264
00:18:41,711 --> 00:18:46,211
Iya, mulai jam sembilan pagi.

265
00:18:46,234 --> 00:18:49,615
Wah, berat ya.

266
00:18:49,639 --> 00:18:53,226
Selesainya jam berapa?

267
00:18:53,249 --> 00:18:57,034
Selesainya jam dua siang.

268
00:18:57,058 --> 00:19:02,091
Kalau gitu, sore kamu ada waktu, ya.

269
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:08,181
Iya. Sore aku mau bersih-bersih dan cuci baju.

270
00:19:08,203 --> 00:19:12,637
Aku bantu bersihin kamarmu, ya.

271
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:15,371
Benarkah?

272
00:19:15,395 --> 00:19:18,153
Terima kasih.

273
00:19:18,176 --> 00:19:23,743
Iya, soalnya kamu selalu masakin aku.

274
00:19:23,766 --> 00:19:26,315
Terima kasih, sangat membantu.

275
00:19:26,338 --> 00:19:31,910
Kalau gitu, besok jam tiga kita bersihin bareng, yuk.

276
00:19:31,933 --> 00:19:34,666
Baiklah.

277
00:19:34,689 --> 00:19:39,356
Kamu sudah lihat prakiraan cuaca hari ini?

278
00:19:39,379 --> 00:19:45,515
Sudah, katanya besok cuacanya cerah banget.

279
00:19:45,538 --> 00:19:49,679
Pakaian yang dicuci pasti cepat kering, ya.

280
00:19:49,703 --> 00:19:52,136
Iya, betul.

281
00:19:52,159 --> 00:19:55,992
Baik, saya akan mematikan lampunya.

282
00:19:56,015 --> 00:19:59,954
Iya. Selamat tidur.

283
00:19:59,978 --> 00:20:02,617
Selamat tidur.

284
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:05,340
Sampai besok.